data.description: Welcome to your new home across the street from the prestigious Winding River Golf Course! This property boasts the perfect blend of privacy, space, and convenience to the nearby amenities of the city.    With three bedrooms and two baths, this charmer represents the best of mid-century design: hardwood floor grace an interior awaiting your own personal design aesthetic. The spacious basement presents endless possibilities - a potential entertainment haven or the ultimate personal retreat.    Situated on nearly two acres of land, this property offers ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. The classic brick exterior not only exudes durability but also adds a touch of timeless sophistication.    Key updates include a replaced septic system in 2016 and newly installed siding on the back "bump out" of the home.  The convenience of a three-car garage ensures ample space for vehicles and storage, adding practicality to this picturesque and partially-fenced abode.  Check out recent comps in the immediate area.  Lots of potential for sweat equity.  Please allow two hours notice for showings.
